{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"0":"The Book of the Sunnah"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":128,"arabicnumber":128,"text":"حدثنا علي بن محمد، حدثنا وكيع، عن اسماعيل، عن قيس، قال رايت يد طلحة شلاء وقى بها رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يوم احد","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":128}}]}